{id:"spell-spiritual-weapon",name:"Spiritual Weapon",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Spiritual Weapon"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Level",content:"2"},{title:"Casting Time",content:"1 bonus action"},{title:"Range",content:"60 feet"},{title:"Components",content:"V, S"},{title:"Duration",content:"1 minute"},{title:"School",content:"Evocation"},{title:"Attack",content:"melee"},{title:"Damage",content:"Force"}]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"Effect"},{id:"MultiText",content:["You create a floating, spectral weapon within range that lasts for the duration or until you cast this spell again. When you cast the spell, you can make a melee spell attack against a creature within 5 feet of the weapon. On a hit, the target takes force damage equal to 1d8 + your spellcasting ability modifier.","As a bonus action on your turn, you can move the weapon up to 20 feet and repeat the attack against a creature within 5 feet of it.","The weapon can take whatever form you choose. Clerics of deities who are associated with a particular weapon (as St. Cuthbert is known for his mace and Thor for his hammer) make this spell's effect resemble that weapon."]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"At higher levels"},{id:"MultiText",content:["When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for every two slot levels above the 2nd."]},{id:"Table",content:[["slot level","2","3","4","5","6","7","8","9"],["damage","1d8 + MOD","1d8 + MOD","2d8 + MOD","2d8 + MOD","3d8 + MOD","3d8 + MOD","4d8 + MOD","4d8 + MOD"]]}]}